{"tid":2402360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人享受和韓國狗同樣插肛門的高級待遇！","createTime":"2021-02-10T11:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T13:37:29.000Z","uid":337052,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"215c3decd28a8700356d73a14317d1a3c9c34c14","tid":2402360,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">韓國首爾首次對寵物狗肛拭子採樣</span></strong><br />\n來源：中國新聞網<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-10 19:24<br />\n<br />\n據韓國首爾市10日通報，一名確診患者的寵物狗出現發燒、流鼻涕等症狀，當天從該寵物狗鼻腔、直腸等處採取了樣本進行檢測。這是首爾市首次對寵物狗進行新冠病毒核酸檢測。今年1月，韓國首次出現寵物確診病例，一隻在慶尚南道的寵物貓被確診感染。韓國防疫部門表示，目前沒有明確證據顯示動物會將新冠肺炎病毒傳染給人類。 (記者 曾鼐）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/d03d256e1c720321527f3ebeec9dcd2fu1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2Fd03d256e1c720321527f3ebeec9dcd2fu1.png&h=ca91b1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/e14e939c79d3686271aa87369745e004u5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2Fe14e939c79d3686271aa87369745e004u5.jpg&h=5d087e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：樊羽瑋"},{"pid":"79c93cfaa360dba11b2eb151731a4a8eb8a411b2","tid":2402360,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"有名你叫支那賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4a3b3e07b8e4b0790a834798cb21b60153710d","tid":2402360,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79c93cfaa360dba11b2eb151731a4a8eb8a411b2","tid":2402360,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"有名你叫支那賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"算是高級動物"},{"pid":"3275076dea44a3704b26e33579eb69a79f6fdca3","tid":2402360,"uid